title: Star Wars The Force Awakens English Audio ONLY
description:
This is English Audio for this movie. This is ONLY the audio.I uploaded this so that someone can sync it with the first CAM that appears.
 This was recorded with a zoom H1 on automatic settings. I was going to include a sample, but it's hardly a huge file. It was recored in a cinema so it sounds a little hollow. It was recorded with auto levels, so sudden loud noises cause a small amount of clipping. Other than that, you can hear what's being said, and it will make a perfectly serviceable English release until someone snags a line recording
